high_descs: Turn round right and go to the bathtub in the bathroom.
Pick a alarmclock from the bath tub.
Come away from bath room and turn right enter the reading room near by to the desklamp.
Turn on the desklamp and check the soap.
anns.task_desc: Pick a bathing AlarmClock from the bath tub and check it under DeskLamp in the reading room.

high_descs: Turn right, move three steps forward, turn right, go forward through the corridor, turn right to enter the toilet, go near the bathtub, turn left, move two steps forward and turn right.
Pick up the alarmclock from the bath tub.
Turn left, move two steps forward, turn right and enter the corridor, turn left, move three steps forward, turn right to enter a room and go near the desklamp.
anns.task_desc: Bring AlarmClock from the bath tub and switch on the DeskLamp on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the bathtub.
Pick up alarm clock from the desk.
Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the desk lamp on your right.
anns.task_desc: Examine a alarm clock by the light of a desk lamp.
